Executive Profile
Joseph A. De Perio  Vice Chairman and President, ROI Acquisition Corp. IIAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 5 Board Members in 5 different organizations across 5 different industries.See Board Relationships39--
Background

		Mr. Joseph A. De Perio has been the President at ROI Acquisition Corp. II since June 28, 2013. Mr. De Perio has been a Senior Member of the portfolio management team of Clinton Group, Inc. since October 2010. He has over 12 years experience in corporate finance, including over 9 years as an investment analyst and portfolio manager in private equity and public equity. He has a strong understanding of corporate finance and strategic business planning activities. He served ... as Portfolio Manager of Clinton Group, Inc. from 2006 to December 2007 and joined Clinton Group in 2006. He served as a Vice Chairman and President of ROI Acquisition Corp. since September 19, 2011. He held positions at Millennium Management LLC and served as an Associate at Trimaran Capital Partners. Prior to this, he served as an Associate and an Analyst in the Mergers and Acquisitions Group at CIBC World Markets Corp. He has been the Non Executive Chairman of the Board at Imation Corp. since August 20, 2015. He has been a Vice Chairman of the Board at ROI Acquisition Corp. II since June 28, 2013. He has been a Director of ROI Acquisition Corp. II since June 28, 2013 and EveryWare Global, Inc. since September 19, 2011. He has been an Independent Director of Imation Corp. since May 20, 2015 and Overland Storage Inc. since April 6, 2011. He served as a Director of Viking Systems Inc., from June 9, 2011 to October 2012. Mr. De Perio received a B.A. in Business Economics from Brown University, graduating with honors.Read Full Background




