Joseph A. de Perio

Age : 38Public asset : 139,638 USDLinked companies :  Glassbridge Enterprises Inc -  ROI Acquisition Corp II 





Summary 



Mr. Joseph A. De Perio is Non-Executive Chairman at Imation Corp., Vice Chairman & President at ROI Acquisition Corp. II and Senior Portfolio Manager at Clinton Group, Inc.He is on the Board of Directors at ROI Acquisition Corp. II and EveryWare Global, Inc. Mr. De Perio was previously employed as an Independent Director by Viking Systems, Inc., an Independent Director by Overland Storage, Inc., Vice Chairman & President by ROI Acquisition Corp., an Analyst by Millennium Management LLC, a Principal by Clinton Group, Inc., Associate of Private Equity by Trimaran Capital Partners LLC, and Associate & Analyst by CIBC Oppenheimer Corp. Mr. De Perio received his undergraduate degree from Brown University.



